title: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet is not producing expected output
description: Bug 49235: The ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet method is not producing the expected output. The output is showing "MySomeClass", but I was expecting it to show "MySomeClass". This issue is not addressed yet by the Servlet 3.0 specification. My code was working fine on Glassfish 3.0.
